\begin{frame}{Remarks}
\begin{itemize}
    \item The QCD+WJets purities obtanined for all the control regions are in general high.
    \item We have estimated QCD+Wjets for all the three years.
    \item We have to complete the analysis with other tests in order to validate this proposal.
\end{itemize}
 
\end{frame}
